ria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xjr1665702753919.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xjr1665702753919.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xjr1665702753919.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xjr1665702753919\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      CLSID\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Internal class ID of the COM component. It is automatically provided when the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">ProgID</span> is selected.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xjr1665702753919__section_qnn_v21_dxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d629117e54\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xjr1665702753919__p_d110765e1_d110766e1_d110767e1\">Once the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">ProgID</span> property is\n        exited, the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">CLSID</span> field is updated with the internal class ID of the\n        ProgID.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xjr1665702753919__p_d110768e1_d110769e1_d110770e1\">Alternatively, you can enter a 32-hex-digit CLSID\n        directly to confirm that the correct ProgID is entered.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xjr1665702753919__p_d110771e1_d110772e1_d110773e1\">If a ProgID is not valid, the CLSID is set to\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;Unknown ProgID&gt;</code>, and the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">CLSID</span> and\n          <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Bind To</span> fields are unavailable.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xjr1665702753919__p_d110774e1_d110775e1_d110776e1\">If the COM Connector is not available, the CLSID is\n        set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;COM Driver not available&gt;</code>, and both the\n          <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">CLSID</span> and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Bind To</span> fields are dimmed.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xjr1665702753919__section_hxq_w21_dxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d629117e96\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xjr1665702753919__ul_wr1_bf1_dxb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xjr1665702753919__li_d42728e1_d42729e1_d42730e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qnm1665702714020.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qnm1665702714020.html\" title=\"A Signature Implementation is a Development Object that defines the technology used to implement a signature, such as Uniface, COM, SOAP and so on. A Signature can have multiple implementations. Each Signature Implementation captures the technology-specific properties of the Signature, Signature Operation, and Signature Parameters.\">Signature Implementation</a> (COM) </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tzb1665702753850.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ProgID</a><p>Name of the COM ProgID.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616957\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616957\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "CLSID Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 CLSID Internal class ID of the COM component. It is automatically provided when the ProgID is selected. Description Once the ProgID property is exited, the CLSID field is updated with the internal class ID of the ProgID. Alternatively, you can enter a 32-hex-digit CLSID directly to confirm that the correct ProgID is entered. If a ProgID is not valid, the CLSID is set to <Unknown ProgID> , and the CLSID and Bind To fields are unavailable. If the COM Connector is not available, the CLSID is set to <COM Driver not available> , and both the CLSID and Bind To fields are dimmed. Applies To Signature Implementation (COM) Related Links ProgID Name of the COM ProgID. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}